}

###

# Get User By Id
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/14e197b3-3648-49bf-9629-c1fee4fe5fac

###

# Get User Balance
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/14e197b3-3648-49bf-9629-c1fee4fe5fac/balance

###

